# Skills directory

The **default directory for all skills** in this project is the repo root **`skills/`** folder.

- Put every skill (existing and newly built) under `skills/<skill-name>/`.
- Each skill has its own folder with `SKILL.md`, optional `reference.md`, `requirements.txt`, and `scripts/` as needed.
- Do not use `.cursor/skills/` for new skills; the canonical location is `skills/` at the project root.

Example: `skills/format-book-agent/SKILL.md`, `skills/orchestrator-agent/SKILL.md`, etc.
